WEBVTT

00:02.320 --> 00:04.560
<i>Is there anything else
that you haven't told us</i>

00:04.560 --> 00:06.840
<i>that might be rather important?</i>

00:06.840 --> 00:08.120
<i>No.</i>

00:08.120 --> 00:09.720
<i>Shame we had to let him go. Mm.</i>

00:09.720 --> 00:11.760
<i>CPS think we don't have
enough yet.</i>

00:11.760 --> 00:13.520
<i>I lied to the police
when I told them</i>

00:13.520 --> 00:15.240
<i>that you came home around midnight.</i>

00:15.240 --> 00:17.120
<i>I checked the clock, it was 4:30.</i>

00:17.120 --> 00:19.680
<i>No, I hurt people in dreams, Joe.
I do bad things, but...</i>

00:19.680 --> 00:21.600
<i>But I know that you know
I'm not bad, mate.</i>

00:21.600 --> 00:23.720
<i>I didn't meet with Catherine,
I met with Cara.</i>

00:23.720 --> 00:26.040
<i>Get out!</i>

00:26.040 --> 00:28.120
<i>You served up Bobby Moran
to divert our attention.</i>

00:28.120 --> 00:29.320
<i>Please get off, I'm not well!</i>

00:29.320 --> 00:32.040
<i>I'm arresting you on suspicion
of the murder of Catherine McCain.</i>

00:32.040 --> 00:34.720
<i>Bobby Moran has a cast-iron alibi,
so, clearly, it's not him.</i>

00:34.720 --> 00:37.240
<i>He is involved somehow.
I know he is.</i>

00:37.240 --> 00:39.880
<i>You were beyond angry.
And you killed her like</i>

00:39.880 --> 00:41.680
<i>the demented actions...
You have nothing!</i>

00:41.680 --> 00:44.320
<i>I know nothing about Catherine.
Stop going on about it.</i>

00:44.320 --> 00:45.960
<i>You have been telling me
a pack of lies.</i>

00:45.960 --> 00:48.680
<i>Isn't that your job? To work out
what's true and what isn't?</i>

00:48.680 --> 00:51.880
<i>He'll try and convince everyone that
he's the one that's being set up.</i>

00:51.880 --> 00:54.240
<i>He might even try and convince
himself that he's innocent.</i>

00:54.240 --> 00:57.440
<i>But he'll slip up,
and we'll have him.</i>

01:11.000 --> 01:13.360
<i>HE GRUNTS</i>

01:35.840 --> 01:37.120
<i>HE EXHALES DEEPLY</i>

01:48.400 --> 01:51.480
<i>CUTLERY RATTLING</i>

01:53.360 --> 01:55.240
<i>APPLIANCE BEEPS, WHIRS</i>

02:02.480 --> 02:06.000
<i>BUBBLING LIQUID</i>

02:07.000 --> 02:09.600
<i>Oh! God!
Oh, sorry.</i>

02:10.680 --> 02:13.680
<i>Sorry, darling, that was my fault.
I should've given you the heads-up.</i>

02:13.680 --> 02:16.120
<i>Yeah, this is um...
This is Joe.</i>

02:16.120 --> 02:17.320
<i>Hi.</i>

02:17.320 --> 02:20.360
<i>He's an old friend
who is a bit down on his luck</i>

02:20.360 --> 02:21.640
<i>at the moment so... Well...</i>

02:21.640 --> 02:24.840
<i>Hello, Joe, I'm Sarah.</i>

02:24.840 --> 02:26.320
<i>I'm sorry about your luck.</i>

02:27.440 --> 02:28.920
<i>It's all right.</i>

02:30.720 --> 02:32.920
<i>When's Daddy coming home?</i>

02:32.920 --> 02:34.920
<i>I don't know, sweetheart.</i>

02:34.920 --> 02:37.040
<i>I've spoken to Mrs Palmer.</i>

02:37.040 --> 02:39.320
<i>Why does she have to know?</i>

02:39.320 --> 02:40.840
<i>Good morning.</i>

02:40.840 --> 02:43.960
<i>Because some people are talking
about Daddy</i>

02:43.960 --> 02:46.240
<i>cos the police made a mistake</i>

02:46.240 --> 02:50.200
<i>and if anyone teases you about it,
I want the teachers to sort it,</i>

02:50.200 --> 02:52.360
<i>and I want them to take care of you.</i>

02:53.480 --> 02:55.320
<i>I could just be with you.</i>

02:55.320 --> 02:57.840
<i>Well, I've got work
and you've got school.</i>

02:59.240 --> 03:00.680
<i>You know how much we love you.</i>

03:00.680 --> 03:02.440
<i>Mwah!</i>

03:02.440 --> 03:05.360
<i>Daddy and I will sort this out. OK.</i>

03:07.560 --> 03:09.280
<i>SCHOOL BELL RINGING</i>

03:09.280 --> 03:10.480
<i>SHE GRUNTS</i>

03:20.560 --> 03:22.120
<i>Her flat mate has told us</i>

03:22.120 --> 03:23.920
<i>that Catherine was seeing a man
in London.</i>

03:23.920 --> 03:27.080
<i>Another of Catherine's co-workers
has corroborated that.</i>

03:27.080 --> 03:29.480
<i>O'Loughlin denies any contact
with Catherine</i>

03:29.480 --> 03:30.680
<i>in the last five years.</i>

03:30.680 --> 03:33.000
<i>If he's the mystery man...</i>

03:33.000 --> 03:34.280
<i>how'd they communicate?</i>

03:34.280 --> 03:36.760
<i>We pulled his phone records
and hers, there's nothing there.</i>

03:36.760 --> 03:39.160
<i>Well, go through them again,</i>

03:39.160 --> 03:42.400
<i>chase every call he's made
in the last five years,</i>

03:42.400 --> 03:45.280
<i>just in case he slipped up. Sir.</i>

03:45.280 --> 03:47.840
<i>Her flatmate, Carl Ashley,</i>

03:47.840 --> 03:51.760
<i>he said that Catherine
kept her affair "close to her...</i>

03:51.760 --> 03:53.400
<i>"like a comfort".
PHONE BUZZING</i>

03:53.400 --> 03:55.600
<i>She enjoyed the secret.</i>

03:55.600 --> 03:57.960
<i>That's how O'Loughlin
manipulated her. Hello?</i>

03:57.960 --> 03:59.440
<i>The importance of the secret.</i>

03:59.440 --> 04:02.160
<i>He probably used a couple of burners
for them to talk.</i>

04:03.880 --> 04:06.480
<i>But Catherine applying
for the job as his secretary</i>

04:06.480 --> 04:09.840
<i>and then ringing the office
that night... was against the rules.</i>

04:09.840 --> 04:11.400
<i>Thank you.</i>

04:11.400 --> 04:13.040
<i>That was one of our door knockers.</i>

04:13.040 --> 04:15.040
<i>A neighbour saw O'Loughlin
burying something</i>

04:15.040 --> 04:16.840
<i>in his back garden a couple
of nights ago.</i>

04:16.840 --> 04:18.520
<i>The murder weapon?</i>

04:18.520 --> 04:20.880
<i>Let's break out the shovels.
Let's go.</i>

04:20.880 --> 04:24.520
<i>Right?
The rest of you, be... better!</i>

04:45.960 --> 04:47.280
<i>Did you tell Julianne?</i>

04:47.280 --> 04:48.840
<i>Yeah.</i>

04:48.840 --> 04:50.360
<i>And?</i>

04:51.800 --> 04:54.400
<i>Yeah, not good. Ah...</i>

04:54.400 --> 04:57.080
<i>Well, you'd just had the worst day
of your life,</i>

04:57.080 --> 04:58.960
<i>so you slept with a friend
in a moment of crisis.</i>

04:58.960 --> 05:00.240
<i>She threw me out.</i>

05:02.600 --> 05:04.080
<i>Don't blame her.</i>

05:04.080 --> 05:06.280
<i>Just got to give her some space.</i>

05:06.280 --> 05:09.040
<i>Well, don't expect me to agree
that we did anything wrong,</i>

05:09.040 --> 05:11.000
<i>I liked being that close to you.</i>

05:11.000 --> 05:13.760
<i>Can we not tell her
that I took advantage of you?</i>

05:13.760 --> 05:16.160
<i>No, no, no, no.
I knew what I was doing.</i>

05:20.280 --> 05:23.320
<i>So, only Julianne knows that
we were together that night,</i>

05:23.320 --> 05:24.560
<i>I haven't told the police.</i>

05:25.600 --> 05:26.840
<i>Do we have to?</i>

05:26.840 --> 05:30.880
<i>Well, I want them to rule me out
of their investigation, so...</i>

05:30.880 --> 05:32.080
<i>OK?</i>

05:33.360 --> 05:35.440
<i>And you're the only alibi I've got.</i>

05:35.440 --> 05:38.160
<i>I'm-I'm so sorry, Cara, I...
Oh, no, no.</i>

05:38.160 --> 05:40.200
<i>There must be another way.</i>

05:40.200 --> 05:42.480
<i>I can't go back into another
interview room,</i>

05:42.480 --> 05:44.280
<i>you know I can't do that...
I'm really sorry.</i>

05:44.280 --> 05:46.600
<i>I'll make sure they understand
the trauma</i>

05:46.600 --> 05:48.480
<i>you've been through before...
"Trauma"?</i>

05:48.480 --> 05:49.840
<i>Which one?</i>

05:49.840 --> 05:51.440
<i>Fighting off the six men
who raped me?</i>

05:51.440 --> 05:53.920
<i>Or being sent to prison
for hurting one of them?</i>

05:53.920 --> 05:56.400
<i>No, I can't!
They, they won't believe me anyways.</i>

05:56.400 --> 05:57.720
<i>Cara, unless I've an alibi</i>

05:57.720 --> 06:00.640
<i>for where I was between ten
and four that night... What...</i>

06:00.640 --> 06:04.680
<i>But you left way before that,
you were gone by 12:30.</i>

06:04.680 --> 06:06.600
<i>But I didn't leave!</i>

06:06.600 --> 06:08.240
<i>I didn't.
I was outside on the steps,</i>

06:08.240 --> 06:10.760
<i>I was there for hours,
trying to get my head together,</i>

06:10.760 --> 06:12.680
<i>and then I... I walked home.</i>

06:12.680 --> 06:14.520
<i>But I didn't see any of that.</i>

06:17.440 --> 06:20.200
<i>Joe, are you asking me to lie
to the police?</i>

06:24.800 --> 06:26.200
<i>No.</i>

06:27.960 --> 06:30.240
<i>No. No, no.
Of course not.</i>

06:36.040 --> 06:37.760
<i>POLICE SIREN CHIRPS</i>

06:39.720 --> 06:40.920
<i>CAR DOOR CLOSES</i>

06:43.040 --> 06:46.000
<i>POLICE RADIO CHATTER</i>

06:46.000 --> 06:48.160
<i>It was a goldfish!</i>

06:48.160 --> 06:51.120
<i>My husband, he buried
our daughter's goldfish.</i>

06:51.120 --> 06:52.920
<i>In the middle of the night?</i>

06:52.920 --> 06:56.800
<i>I don't know when he did it,
I just know he did.</i>

07:01.840 --> 07:03.200
<i>I'm, er...</i>

07:03.200 --> 07:04.560
<i>sorry to add to your troubles,</i>

07:04.560 --> 07:07.040
<i>but I've had to turn the water off
for a couple of hours.</i>

07:08.760 --> 07:12.520
<i>I could go out with a shovel,
put it right when they've finished.</i>

07:12.520 --> 07:15.960
<i>That's kind of you, but...
it's all right.</i>

07:15.960 --> 07:18.120
<i>CAMERA SHUTTER SNAPS</i>

07:19.720 --> 07:21.520
<i>Do you want some coffee?</i>

07:21.520 --> 07:23.160
<i>You always say no to mine.</i>

07:24.280 --> 07:25.920
<i>Taste this, you'll see why.</i>

07:42.120 --> 07:44.440
<i>Can I get a couple more
bags here, please?</i>

07:46.200 --> 07:47.720
<i>It's all right, innit?</i>

07:47.720 --> 07:49.520
<i>Yeah, I see why.
SHE CHUCKLES</i>

07:49.520 --> 07:50.960
<i>Sir! I found something.</i>

07:53.040 --> 07:55.280
<i>CAMERA SHUTTER SNAPS, WHIRS</i>

07:57.720 --> 08:00.120
<i>Now do you believe me?</i>

08:00.120 --> 08:02.640
<i>That's an old jewellery box of mine.</i>

08:02.640 --> 08:04.480
<i>I told you, a goldfish.</i>

08:04.480 --> 08:08.000
<i>Mrs O'Loughlin,
have you had any further thoughts?</i>

08:09.320 --> 08:10.800
<i>About what?</i>

08:10.800 --> 08:13.000
<i>The exact time that your husband
came home that night.</i>

08:13.000 --> 08:15.400
<i>Did you talk to him -
about where he'd been?</i>

08:15.400 --> 08:17.360
<i>I have nothing more to add.</i>

08:23.600 --> 08:25.480
<i>A loyal but lying wife?</i>

08:25.480 --> 08:28.480
<i>I think he may have played us again,
you know.</i>

08:28.480 --> 08:30.480
<i>He does something
completely innocent,</i>

08:30.480 --> 08:32.360
<i>he buries
his daughter's dead goldfish,</i>

08:32.360 --> 08:33.760
<i>but he does it at night,</i>

08:33.760 --> 08:35.720
<i>knowing his security light
will bang on,</i>

08:35.720 --> 08:39.240
<i>and if he makes enough noise
a neighbour's gonna take a look,</i>

08:39.240 --> 08:41.800
<i>and think he's up to no good,
so they tell us.</i>

08:41.800 --> 08:44.240
<i>We show up... with the circus</i>

08:44.240 --> 08:47.160
<i>to catch the killer
and we prove to everyone</i>

08:47.160 --> 08:50.360
<i>that O'Loughlin is just an innocent,
hounded victim.</i>

08:55.960 --> 08:57.960
<i>Yeah.</i>

08:57.960 --> 08:59.920
<i>Yeah, she's lying.</i>

09:02.200 --> 09:04.640
<i>He'll be manipulating everyone
around him,</i>

09:04.640 --> 09:07.200
<i>trying to convince them
of his innocence.</i>

09:13.640 --> 09:15.440
<i>What are you up to?</i>

09:15.440 --> 09:20.160
<i>Going through Bobby Moran's
heath records and my notes on him.</i>

09:20.160 --> 09:23.160
<i>God, I... I've still no idea
who he is</i>

09:23.160 --> 09:25.200
<i>or how he's involved
in Catherine's murder.</i>

09:25.200 --> 09:26.760
<i>What's his diagnosis?</i>

09:26.760 --> 09:29.880
<i>I've been thinking
Dissociative Identity Disorder.</i>

09:29.880 --> 09:31.400
<i>Could explain the lying,</i>

09:31.400 --> 09:33.320
<i>unpredictable change of behaviour</i>

09:33.320 --> 09:35.280
<i>and personality,
the different voices...</i>

09:35.280 --> 09:37.000
<i>But you're not sure.</i>

09:37.000 --> 09:38.800
<i>No.</i>

09:38.800 --> 09:40.680
<i>I'd need more sessions with him.</i>

09:40.680 --> 09:42.960
<i>Well, you're not allowed
to go anywhere near him.</i>

09:42.960 --> 09:45.080
<i>I just think somebody's
manipulating him.</i>

09:45.080 --> 09:47.080
<i>It's the only explanation.</i>

09:47.080 --> 09:48.480
<i>I just need to find out who it is.</i>

09:57.400 --> 09:58.840
<i>Rache.</i>

09:58.840 --> 10:00.240
<i>Mm?
Have a look at this.</i>

10:00.240 --> 10:03.240
<i>I've just checked his patient file
with his hospital number.</i>

10:03.240 --> 10:04.600
<i>Look.</i>

10:06.080 --> 10:08.560
<i>He's two sets of records.</i>

10:08.560 --> 10:09.920
<i>What do you mean?</i>

10:09.920 --> 10:12.640
<i>He's registered
under a different name.</i>

10:12.640 --> 10:15.760
<i>His name isn't Bobby Moran.
It's Bobby Morgan.</i>

10:15.760 --> 10:17.760
<i>That could just be
a simple spelling mistake.</i>

10:17.760 --> 10:19.520
<i>Duplicate records happen
all the time.</i>

10:19.520 --> 10:23.240
<i>No, no, no. It's more than that,
it's the pattern to his lying,</i>

10:23.240 --> 10:26.760
<i>things are... almost right,
but they're not.</i>

10:26.760 --> 10:29.560
<i>He changed one letter.
I've seen this before in patients,</i>

10:29.560 --> 10:31.920
<i>they do it to keep their lies
in order.</i>

10:31.920 --> 10:37.160
<i>Look, this is his first referral
letter to the hospital.</i>

10:37.160 --> 10:38.800
<i>Joe, are you sure this is ethical?</i>

10:38.800 --> 10:41.320
<i>Not entirely,
but he's been lying to me.</i>

10:41.320 --> 10:44.000
<i>Look, he's not from London,
he's from Liverpool.</i>

10:44.000 --> 10:46.440
<i>That's his connection
to Catherine McCain, Liverpool!</i>

10:46.440 --> 10:48.400
<i>Oh, my God.
Isn't that where you trained?</i>

10:48.400 --> 10:51.960
<i>Yeah. All these names
and places he talked about,</i>

10:51.960 --> 10:53.920
<i>I think some of them might be real.</i>

10:54.920 --> 10:56.320
<i>I need to go there,</i>

10:56.320 --> 10:58.040
<i>talk to the people
that he spoke about,</i>

10:58.040 --> 11:00.560
<i>and see if there's some tangible
connection to Catherine...</i>

11:00.560 --> 11:01.800
<i>Joe, you've been arrested</i>

11:01.800 --> 11:03.600
<i>and cautioned on suspicion
of murder,</i>

11:03.600 --> 11:05.600
<i>you can't go around talking
to witnesses.</i>

11:05.600 --> 11:07.200
<i>It will make you look
even more guilty.</i>

11:07.200 --> 11:10.640
<i>Rachel, the police are fixed on me,
they're not looking for the truth.</i>

11:10.640 --> 11:12.800
<i>I need to find it.</i>

11:12.800 --> 11:15.360
<i>I've got to prove Bobby's lying
and not me.</i>

11:18.840 --> 11:21.680
<i>PHONE BUZZING, CHIMING</i>

11:21.680 --> 11:25.240
<i>Sorry, er... can you just give me
a sec?</i>

11:27.160 --> 11:29.200
<i>PHONE RINGING TONE</i>

11:29.200 --> 11:30.800
<i>'Er... Hey, Joe.'
Hi.</i>

11:30.800 --> 11:33.400
<i>'The police have been round here,
wanting to talk to you, um...'</i>

11:33.400 --> 11:36.520
<i>Where are you?
'Back in our old stomping ground.'</i>

11:36.520 --> 11:39.240
<i>I'm in Liverpool.
'Er, why? Why are you there?'</i>

11:39.240 --> 11:40.840
<i>So, listen to this,</i>

11:40.840 --> 11:44.280
<i>Bobby Moran's real name
is Bobby Morgan</i>

11:44.280 --> 11:46.880
<i>'and his family live here.</i>

11:46.880 --> 11:48.760
<i>'Do you remember anything more
about him?</i>

11:48.760 --> 11:50.720
<i>'Any little details?</i>

11:50.720 --> 11:53.320
<i>Your referral letter to me
doesn't give me the name of his GP</i>

11:53.320 --> 11:55.040
<i>or his medical history.</i>

11:55.040 --> 11:57.960
<i>I ju... All I remember is con...
like, confusion and headaches,</i>

11:57.960 --> 11:59.680
<i>but you know people.</i>

11:59.680 --> 12:02.600
<i>You know, people change their names
and their history all the time.</i>

12:02.600 --> 12:05.680
<i>Yeah, you see, I think somebody
helped him con his way to you,</i>

12:05.680 --> 12:07.360
<i>knowing you were a route to me.</i>

12:07.360 --> 12:08.600
<i>'Really? That sounds, er...'</i>

12:08.600 --> 12:09.840
<i>a little far-fetched, Joe.</i>

12:09.840 --> 12:12.280
<i>I mean, why go through me,
why not go straight to you?</i>

12:12.280 --> 12:14.200
<i>So he doesn't come out of nowhere,</i>

12:14.200 --> 12:15.840
<i>makes for a better lie.</i>

12:15.840 --> 12:17.760
<i>Joe, what are you gonna do?</i>

12:17.760 --> 12:19.520
<i>'Some basic psychology.</i>

12:19.520 --> 12:23.440
<i>'I'm gonna talk to all the people
Bobby spoke about from his past.'</i>

12:23.440 --> 12:25.280
<i>Find out...</i>

12:25.280 --> 12:28.080
<i>who he is, his link to Catherine,</i>

12:28.080 --> 12:29.560
<i>and why he's got me involved.</i>

12:29.560 --> 12:31.840
<i>'And then maybe I can begin
to save my marriage.'</i>

12:31.840 --> 12:34.200
<i>OK, Joe, listen, I really don't
think this is a good idea.</i>

12:34.200 --> 12:37.160
<i>If you do think of anything, Jack,
let me know.</i>

12:37.160 --> 12:39.480
<i>And if the police call you,</i>

12:39.480 --> 12:40.840
<i>don't tell them where I am.</i>

12:40.840 --> 12:42.800
<i>'I'm treading a fine line
right now.'</i>

12:42.800 --> 12:46.280
<i>Look, look, Jack, I-I gotta go.
'Wait, Joe...'</i>

12:47.520 --> 12:50.600
<i>Hey! It's getting cold.</i>

12:54.360 --> 12:56.320
<i>Yep, yep.</i>

12:56.320 --> 12:57.480
<i>OK.</i>

12:57.480 --> 13:00.320
<i>POLICE SIREN ECHOING</i>

13:10.760 --> 13:13.560
<i>Don't you have a home to go to?
Don't you?</i>

13:16.160 --> 13:18.240
<i>It's, um...</i>

13:18.240 --> 13:20.120
<i>It's a knock-back.</i>

13:20.120 --> 13:22.520
<i>They won't go for a court order
to give us access</i>

13:22.520 --> 13:24.320
<i>to O'Loughlin's past client list.</i>

13:24.320 --> 13:26.600
<i>Not unless we produce more evidence.</i>

13:40.360 --> 13:42.080
<i>What she went through,</i>

13:42.080 --> 13:46.040
<i>that was done with a...
practised hand.</i>

13:47.760 --> 13:49.560
<i>She wasn't his first victim.</i>

13:49.560 --> 13:53.600
<i>We've got to find the thing
that nails him.</i>

13:53.600 --> 13:57.720
<i>But do you know what else
is missing... from this case?</i>

14:00.080 --> 14:02.240
<i>No-one's crying out for her.</i>

14:03.680 --> 14:05.800
<i>No-one demanding justice,</i>

14:05.800 --> 14:11.080
<i>just an only child,
no close friends, both parents dead.</i>

14:12.840 --> 14:14.720
<i>We're all she's got.</i>

14:17.880 --> 14:19.160
<i>There we go.
Thank you.</i>

14:19.160 --> 14:22.000
<i>Um... I'm gonna go and get a...</i>

14:22.000 --> 14:24.560
<i>It's dead.
