14:32.280 --> 14:34.560
<i>Just give me a sec.</i>

14:45.400 --> 14:48.120
<i>PHONE RINGING TONE</i>

14:48.120 --> 14:49.200
<i>'Hello?'</i>

14:49.200 --> 14:51.720
<i>Hi, Detective Ruis?
'Yeah.'</i>

14:51.720 --> 14:54.600
<i>Yes, hi, it, um...
it's Dr Gerald Owens, um...</i>

14:55.680 --> 14:57.200
<i>'How can I help you, Dr Owens?'</i>

14:57.200 --> 14:59.240
<i>It's about Dr O'Loughlin.</i>

14:59.240 --> 15:01.000
<i>'I know where he is.'</i>

15:04.360 --> 15:05.760
<i>KNOCK AT DOOR</i>

15:05.760 --> 15:08.720
<i>Miss Elwood, the psychologist
