15:20.640 --> 15:22.720
<i>13 years ago.</i>

15:22.720 --> 15:24.680
<i>I'm not sure I can be of any help.</i>

15:25.760 --> 15:27.920
<i>And I don't think I should.</i>

15:27.920 --> 15:30.640
<i>I have a duty of confidentiality.</i>

