15:42.800 --> 15:45.320
<i>But these are exceptional circumstances.</i>

15:46.240 --> 15:47.960
<i>Bobby's in trouble.</i>

15:47.960 --> 15:50.200
<i>I need to help him in any way I can.</i>

15:50.200 --> 15:54.280
<i>I really don't think that I can...
I know 13 years is a long time,</i>

15:54.280 --> 15:55.960
<i>but...</i>

15:55.960 --> 15:57.560
<i>he does remember a Mrs Elwood</i>

15:57.560 --> 16:01.040
<i>as one of the kind faces
