16:01.040 --> 16:03.240
<i>You're a cherished memory.</i>

16:03.240 --> 16:05.200
<i>He doesn't have too many of those.</i>

16:07.040 --> 16:08.760
<i>Well, I do remember him...</i>

16:10.280 --> 16:12.000
<i>...but I'm sorry.</i>

16:13.240 --> 16:15.480
<i>What do you remember about him?</i>

16:16.840 --> 16:18.560
<i>He had the voice of an angel.</i>

16:18.560 --> 16:22.640
<i>When Bobby was in the choir,
