16:22.640 --> 16:24.720
<i>Everyone stopped to listen.</i>

16:24.720 --> 16:26.760
<i>You had to.</i>

16:26.760 --> 16:28.880
<i>He had a real gift.</i>

16:28.880 --> 16:33.440
<i>Bobby spoke quite lovingly
about his father.</i>

16:33.440 --> 16:35.520
<i>Bobby's father wasn't allowed
in the school.</i>

16:35.520 --> 16:37.720
<i>Because?</i>

16:43.360 --> 16:46.440
<i>At the time,
I was Bobby's form teacher.</i>

16:47.480 --> 16:49.840
<i>He'd wet himself.</i>

16:49.840 --> 16:53.280
<i>I took him to the school nurse
to get a fresh pair of trousers.</i>

16:54.560 --> 16:56.000
<i>She saw the welts.</i>

16:56.960 --> 16:59.280
<i>He'd been beaten, badly.</i>

