<i>It was shut.</i>

18:17.600 --> 18:19.400
<i>Well, I didn't see him
carrying anything,</i>

18:19.400 --> 18:21.960
<i>so I must have disturbed him
before he had the chance.</i>

18:23.440 --> 18:26.600
<i>You should call the police.
I don't think they'll be much help.</i>

18:26.600 --> 18:28.120
<i>Um...</i>

18:28.120 --> 18:29.960
<i>thank god you were here.</i>

18:43.040 --> 18:46.760
<i>PHONE RINGING TONE</i>

18:46.760 --> 18:50.520
<i>PHONE RINGING</i>

18:53.920 --> 18:56.520
<i>Darling, please, don't hang up.</i>

18:56.520 --> 18:58.560
<i>'OK, then I won't.'</i>

18:58.560 --> 19:00.080
<i>Jack?</i>

19:00.080 --> 19:01.800
<i>What are you doing
with Julianne's phone?</i>

19:01.800 --> 19:04.840
<i>'Where are you?'
Um... I'm at your place, buddy.</i>

19:04.840 --> 19:08.040
<i>Oh... OK, well, let me speak to her.</i>

19:08.040 --> 19:11.600
<i>Um... Joe, she, er...
she doesn't want to talk to you.</i>

19:11.600 --> 19:13.640
<i>Actually, buddy, she, um...</i>

19:13.640 --> 19:16.240
<i>Actually, she's...
she just walked out.</i>

19:16.240 --> 19:18.160
<i>Sorry, why-why are you there?</i>

19:18.160 --> 19:20.160
<i>'Julianne didn't wanna be alone. Um...</i>

19:20.160 --> 19:22.120
<i>'Joe, listen someone's tried
