19:22.120 --> 19:23.600
<i>'and she, er... she got spooked,'</i>

19:23.600 --> 19:24.720
<i>and...
'What?'</i>

19:24.720 --> 19:26.880
<i>So, I-I... I offered to come over.</i>

19:26.880 --> 19:29.080
<i>When did this happen?
'It was this morning.'</i>

19:29.080 --> 19:31.080
<i>I think the plumber guy managed
to chase him out,</i>

19:31.080 --> 19:33.440
<i>but, I don't think he got a...
he got a good look him.</i>

19:33.440 --> 19:35.280
<i>'I don't think they took anything,
though.'</i>

19:35.280 --> 19:36.920
<i>Listen to me,
I want to talk to Julianne.</i>

19:36.920 --> 19:38.920
<i>'Mm...'</i>

19:38.920 --> 19:40.200
<i>Jack!</i>

19:40.200 --> 19:42.440
<i>Give her the fucking phone - now!</i>

19:42.440 --> 19:45.320
<i>Joe, buddy, listen to me,
you need to calm down, she...</i>

19:45.320 --> 19:47.160
<i>'just doesn't want to speak
to you right now.'</i>

19:47.160 --> 19:48.800
<i>Give her the fucking phone!
OK, Joe,</i>

19:48.800 --> 19:50.840
<i>listen to me, I'm gonna hang up now
and I need you...</i>

19:50.840 --> 19:52.000
<i>'Don't fucking hang up!'</i>

19:52.000 --> 19:53.640
<i>...to stay calm
and look after yourself.</i>

19:53.640 --> 19:55.240
<i>'Don't hang up,
I need to speak to...'</i>

20:04.840 --> 20:06.360
<i>Hey, kiddo.</i>

20:06.360 --> 20:07.840
<i>You, OK?
Mm-hm.</i>

20:19.560 --> 20:21.680
<i>PHONE BUZZING</i>

20:23.320 --> 20:24.560
<i>Hello?</i>

20:24.560 --> 20:25.800
<i>'Dad, is that you?'</i>

20:25.800 --> 20:28.400
<i>Charlie, how are you, sweetheart?</i>

20:28.400 --> 20:31.040
<i>OK. When are you coming home?</i>

20:31.040 --> 20:32.640
<i>I don't know.</i>

20:32.640 --> 20:35.280
<i>I have a few things to sort out
with your mummy first.</i>

20:35.280 --> 20:37.280
<i>Was it your fault?</i>

20:37.280 --> 20:39.400
<i>Yeah.</i>

20:39.400 --> 20:41.760
<i>Yeah, it was, totally.</i>

20:41.760 --> 20:43.720
<i>Then why don't you just say sorry?</i>

20:43.720 --> 20:45.520
<i>JOE EXHALES DEEPLY</i>

20:45.520 --> 20:48.000
<i>I don't think that's gonna work
this time, love.</i>

20:48.000 --> 20:49.600
<i>At school...</i>

20:49.600 --> 20:51.560
<i>they're saying that you're...</i>

20:51.560 --> 20:53.400
<i>you do bad things.</i>

20:53.400 --> 20:55.880
<i>Yeah, look, Charlie, look,
there's been a mistake.</i>

20:55.880 --> 20:58.120
<i>The police have made a mistake.</i>

20:58.120 --> 21:01.520
<i>'Then why is Mummy angry with you?'</i>

21:01.520 --> 21:04.120
<i>Because I made another mistake.
A different one.</i>

21:04.120 --> 21:05.920
<i>But it has nothing to do
with the police.</i>

21:05.920 --> 21:07.320
<i>Or nothing to do with you.</i>

21:07.320 --> 21:10.120
<i>Feels like it
when Mummy brushes my hair.</i>

21:11.160 --> 21:13.200
<i>Is your mummy all right?</i>

21:13.200 --> 21:16.240
<i>She told Uncle Jack she was late.</i>

21:17.280 --> 21:18.560
<i>Late for what?</i>

21:18.560 --> 21:21.200
<i>'She just said she was late.'</i>

21:21.200 --> 21:24.240
<i>And she was sick too... twice.</i>

21:26.840 --> 21:29.120
<i>'I've gotta put her phone back now, Dad.</i>

21:29.120 --> 21:31.560
<i>'Come home soon, please.</i>

21:31.560 --> 21:33.640
<i>'I love you, Dad.'</i>

21:33.640 --> 21:35.320
<i>I love you too.</i>

21:55.640 --> 21:57.400
<i>So, this is the new management look?</i>

21:57.400 --> 22:02.160
<i>Well, I've been in children's court,
fighting with "my learned friends".</i>

22:03.400 --> 22:04.680
<i>Come here.</i>

22:10.800 --> 22:12.040
<i>Mm.</i>

22:18.080 --> 22:21.200
<i>Hiya. Um, I -I'll just get
an espresso...</i>

22:21.200 --> 22:22.600
<i>OK.
Please, thank you.</i>

22:27.440 --> 22:29.320
<i>Well, of course, I've seen the news.</i>

22:29.320 --> 22:31.800
<i>And they thought that was you.</i>

22:31.800 --> 22:34.160
<i>Yeah. Yeah...</i>

22:34.160 --> 22:36.680
<i>They're not bringing charges
against me.</i>

22:36.680 --> 22:38.640
<i>It was a stupid mistake.</i>

22:38.640 --> 22:39.760
<i>Hmm.</i>

22:42.280 --> 22:43.960
<i>Yeah, I never believed a word of it.</i>

22:46.800 --> 22:48.560
<i>So, how's Julianne?</i>

22:48.560 --> 22:50.040
<i>She's good.
Yeah?</i>

22:50.040 --> 22:51.560
<i>Yeah. Yeah.</i>

22:51.560 --> 22:53.560
<i>How's Boyd?</i>

22:57.160 --> 22:58.760
<i>What?</i>

23:01.040 --> 23:02.480
<i>He died.</i>

23:04.280 --> 23:05.920
<i>Oh, God, I'm so sorry.</i>

23:05.920 --> 23:07.720
<i>It was a year ago.</i>

23:09.160 --> 23:10.680
<i>Er...</i>

23:10.680 --> 23:12.440
<i>Why didn't I tell you?</i>

23:13.800 --> 23:16.760
<i>Because I was angry at you.</i>

23:17.800 --> 23:19.920
<i>I wanted to hurt you.</i>

23:22.120 --> 23:24.280
<i>You never looked back.</i>

23:25.480 --> 23:30.200
<i>You left me and Boyd behind
when you went down to London.</i>

23:30.200 --> 23:32.760
<i>We just disappeared
from your life,</i>

23:32.760 --> 23:36.480
<i>then when he invited you
to his 40th birthday,</i>

23:36.480 --> 23:38.880
<i>you didn't even reply to him.</i>

23:40.840 --> 23:42.720
<i>That hurt him.</i>

23:45.600 --> 23:47.360
<i>That hurt him a lot.</i>

23:50.840 --> 23:52.600
<i>Thank you.</i>

23:56.800 --> 23:58.400
<i>How?</i>

23:59.800 --> 24:01.360
<i>What happened?</i>

24:04.640 --> 24:06.800
<i>A pedestrian crossing.</i>

24:08.000 --> 24:09.720
<i>You know what Boyd was like.</i>

24:09.720 --> 24:14.120
<i>He had right of way,
and he stepped in front of a big...</i>

24:15.160 --> 24:16.920
<i>...a big bastard SUV, and...</i>

24:16.920 --> 24:19.480
<i>Oh, God, Mel, I'm so sorry.</i>

24:22.440 --> 24:26.960
<i>Um... so, Bobby Morgan,
I had a look. Yeah?</i>

24:26.960 --> 24:30.880
<i>Right, he was abused by his dad,
and then I put him into care,</i>

24:30.880 --> 24:33.160
<i>took a court order out
to keep him away from his dad,</i>

24:33.160 --> 24:35.120
<i>and... gave him back to his mum.</i>

24:35.120 --> 24:37.040
<i>Right.</i>

24:37.040 --> 24:38.960
<i>Can I see the red edges?</i>

24:38.960 --> 24:40.920
<i>No, course you can't.</i>

24:42.080 --> 24:44.360
<i>You can't read the files,
you don't work for us any more.</i>

24:44.360 --> 24:46.440
<i>You know the rules.
Yeah, yeah.</i>

24:50.640 --> 24:53.000
<i>Now, tell me...</i>

24:53.000 --> 24:55.520
<i>why you need to know
about Bobby Morgan?</i>

25:18.200 --> 25:21.760
<i>So, I have a case meeting,
I'll be half an hour.</i>

25:21.760 --> 25:23.640
<i>You gonna be all right in here
by yourself?</i>

25:23.640 --> 25:25.360
<i>Yeah.</i>

25:25.360 --> 25:27.080
<i>Thanks.</i>

25:27.080 --> 25:28.920
<i>Mm.</i>

25:45.880 --> 25:48.000
<i>PHONE RINGING TONE</i>

25:48.000 --> 25:51.320
<i>'DI Ruis.'
DC Hegarty, sir.</i>

25:51.320 --> 25:53.000
<i>Yeah, I followed O'Loughlin, yeah,</i>

25:53.000 --> 25:54.960
<i>to the Liverpool social services office.</i>

25:54.960 --> 25:59.200
<i>'He's in with a Melinda Cossimo.
She's one of their social workers.'</i>

25:59.200 --> 26:00.520
<i>Well, wait until he comes out</i>

26:00.520 --> 26:02.760
<i>and then see what he was doing
in there, all right?</i>

26:02.760 --> 26:06.240
<i>So, yesterday was a... school
and the town hall?</i>

26:06.240 --> 26:10.160
<i>Yeah.
Always asking about a Bobby Morgan.</i>

26:10.160 --> 26:14.080
<i>Yeah, he might be trying
to build a false narrative.</i>

26:14.080 --> 26:16.360
<i>I'm coming up to Liverpool.</i>

26:16.360 --> 26:18.840
<i>I just... I wanna be there
when he slips up.</i>

26:18.840 --> 26:20.160
<i>We'll be there tomorrow.</i>

26:20.160 --> 26:22.840
<i>'In the meantime, keep on him.'</i>

26:22.840 --> 26:24.840
<i>Will, do, sir.</i>

26:31.120 --> 26:34.840
<i>CAMERA CLICKS</i>

26:38.040 --> 26:42.320
<i>Yeah... it all points
to sexual abuse from the father.</i>

26:43.520 --> 26:45.840
<i>I didn't get a hint of that
in any of my sessions with Bobby.</i>

26:45.840 --> 26:48.680
<i>He adored his dad.
Well, you know how abusers work.</i>

26:48.680 --> 26:50.280
<i>Yeah...</i>

26:50.280 --> 26:53.640
<i>Yeah, I know there's nothing
to stop an abuser being a...</i>

26:53.640 --> 26:56.680
<i>safe, loving figure, but...</i>

26:57.800 --> 26:59.040
<i>I mean, it could be the reason</i>

26:59.040 --> 27:01.720
<i>why Bobby needs so many different
personalities to survive.</i>

27:03.240 --> 27:05.080
<i>I just don't see how I missed it.</i>

27:06.320 --> 27:08.280
<i>I mean, look at this, right?</i>

27:10.120 --> 27:12.960
<i>Lenny Morgan's first wife died.</i>

27:12.960 --> 27:15.160
<i>They had a son, Dafydd.</i>

27:15.160 --> 27:17.560
<i>Why has he never come to
the attention of social services?</i>

27:17.560 --> 27:19.360
<i>Why was he never interviewed
about Lenny?</i>

27:19.360 --> 27:21.280
<i>Well, we tried,</i>

27:21.280 --> 27:25.760
<i>but he was older than Bobby,
he was...</i>

27:25.760 --> 27:27.960
<i>Yeah.</i>

27:27.960 --> 27:30.320
<i>There. He was 16 at the time.</i>

27:30.320 --> 27:34.120
<i>He left home,
we needed to establish why,</i>

27:34.120 --> 27:37.440
<i>tracked him to Southern Australia,
to a backpacker's hostel,</i>

27:37.440 --> 27:39.440
<i>but he'd left, he'd disappeared.</i>

27:39.440 --> 27:40.800
<i>Hmm.</i>

27:42.200 --> 27:44.920
<i>What was Bobby's mother like?
Oh...</i>

27:44.920 --> 27:47.080
<i>It was 13 years ago.</i>

27:48.200 --> 27:50.520
<i>What I do know is that...</i>

27:50.520 --> 27:53.800
<i>Bobby showed all the classic signs
of being abused.</i>

27:53.800 --> 27:56.080
<i>Do you wanna look at this?
Yeah.</i>

27:56.080 --> 27:59.240
<i>These are Bobby's filmed interviews.</i>

27:59.240 --> 28:00.640
<i>Hmm.</i>

28:00.640 --> 28:02.320
<i>If this thing still works.</i>

28:24.640 --> 28:26.280
<i>'Now, Bobby,
I've a few questions</i>

28:26.280 --> 28:27.320
<i>'to ask you, is that OK?'</i>

28:27.320 --> 28:29.120
<i>I wanna go home.</i>

28:30.160 --> 28:36.360
<i>'Bobby, do you know the difference
between the truth and a lie?'</i>

28:37.400 --> 28:39.240
<i>That's me.</i>

28:39.240 --> 28:41.400
<i>That's my voice!</i>

28:44.080 --> 28:46.360
<i>But it wasn't my case,
I-I'd have remembered him.</i>

28:46.360 --> 28:49.640
<i>Well, you must have sat in
for someone just for that session.</i>

28:51.920 --> 28:53.360
<i>Erskine.</i>

28:53.360 --> 28:55.760
<i>It was his case.
Yeah, but I'm involved.</i>

28:55.760 --> 28:56.800
<i>In what?</i>

28:56.800 --> 28:58.120
<i>I don't know, I-I...</i>

28:58.120 --> 29:00.400
<i>I couldn't have spoken to him
for more than 20 minutes,</i>

29:00.400 --> 29:01.680
<i>13 years ago!</i>

29:01.680 --> 29:03.680
<i>Everything that he was going through,</i>

29:03.680 --> 29:06.280
<i>you would have just been
another face in the crowd,</i>

29:06.280 --> 29:08.320
<i>he wouldn't have remembered you.</i>

29:10.040 --> 29:12.360
<i>Joe, you know
that you cannot use anything</i>

29:12.360 --> 29:14.360
<i>that you have found out today.</i>

29:14.360 --> 29:16.040
<i>Absolutely nothing. Yeah.</i>

29:16.040 --> 29:17.760
<i>Is that clear?
Mm-hm.</i>

29:17.760 --> 29:19.440
<i>Yeah.</i>

29:23.760 --> 29:26.360
<i>GRINDING</i>

29:30.480 --> 29:32.400
<i>Excuse me!</i>

29:32.400 --> 29:34.360
<i>Er... sorry to disturb you, um...</i>

29:34.360 --> 29:36.600
<i>I was wondering if there was
anything you could tell me</i>

29:36.600 --> 29:37.800
<i>about a Lenny Morgan.</i>

29:37.800 --> 29:40.240
<i>Lenny Morgan, Christ,
that's going back a bit.</i>

29:40.240 --> 29:42.280
<i>Anything, anything at all.</i>

29:42.280 --> 29:44.720
<i>Bert McMullen,
that's who you need to talk to.</i>

29:44.720 --> 29:46.840
<i>Him and Lenny were great mates.</i>

29:46.840 --> 29:48.280
<i>Where can I find him?</i>

29:48.280 --> 29:50.360
<i>HE CHUCKLES
In the pub.</i>

30:00.680 --> 30:02.360
<i>Dave.</i>

30:02.360 --> 30:03.480
<i>Ta, mate.</i>

30:11.280 --> 30:14.560
<i>I'll get that... if you don't mind?</i>

30:15.640 --> 30:17.600
<i>It's Bert, right?</i>

30:17.600 --> 30:21.280
<i>I was just at the bus depot,
they said I might find you here.</i>

30:22.440 --> 30:24.880
<i>You were a friend of Lenny Morgan's?</i>

30:24.880 --> 30:27.120
<i>There you go.</i>

30:27.120 --> 30:30.400
<i>I'm trying to help out Lenny's son, Bobby.</i>

30:30.400 --> 30:32.920
<i>He's in a spot of bother. Cheers.</i>

30:36.120 --> 30:37.480
<i>Ta.</i>

30:37.480 --> 30:39.800
<i>What sort of bother?</i>

30:39.800 --> 30:40.960
<i>Assault.</i>

30:40.960 --> 30:43.280
<i>He could go to prison.</i>

30:44.680 --> 30:46.680
<i>I'm looking into anything
to help him.</i>

30:46.680 --> 30:48.760
<i>Family background, friends...</i>

30:48.760 --> 30:51.680
<i>I haven't seen him
since he was a kid.</i>

30:53.840 --> 30:55.920
<i>He was a clever little boy.</i>

30:57.280 --> 30:59.280
<i>Lenny used to bring him
to the depot.</i>

30:59.280 --> 31:00.920
<i>Bobby worshipped his dad.</i>

31:00.920 --> 31:03.680
<i>Yeah. I got that impression.</i>

31:05.440 --> 31:08.120
<i>I've dug around a little bit,
and I know...</i>

31:08.120 --> 31:11.280
<i>Lenny was killed in a fire or...</i>

31:11.280 --> 31:14.040
<i>some kind of explosion
or something, but...</i>

31:14.040 --> 31:16.600
<i>So, why'd you need me, then?</i>

31:17.680 --> 31:19.840
<i>Yeah, er, sorry,
I haven't introduced myself,</i>

31:19.840 --> 31:21.840
<i>I'm-I'm Joe, er...</i>

31:21.840 --> 31:24.320
<i>I'm a psychologist. I'm wor...
Oh, fuck, no. Go home.</i>

31:24.320 --> 31:26.160
<i>Your mother's got custard waiting
for you.</i>

31:29.240 --> 31:31.400
<i>The thing is, Bert,</i>

31:31.400 --> 31:33.560
<i>if Bobby...</i>

31:33.560 --> 31:36.280
<i>was traumatised by the death
of his father,</i>

31:36.280 --> 31:37.400
<i>it could help mitigate...</i>

31:37.400 --> 31:40.040
<i>"Traumatised"? Fuck off.</i>

31:40.040 --> 31:42.240
<i>We were all of us that.</i>

31:43.400 --> 31:46.800
<i>We could have all done
with a bit of "mitigating".</i>

31:49.880 --> 31:51.800
<i>Cheers to that.</i>

31:54.880 --> 31:56.920
<i>Can you tell me
about Bobby's family?</i>

31:58.240 --> 32:00.280
<i>He has difficultly talking
about them.</i>

32:00.280 --> 32:01.840
<i>What was Lenny like?</i>

32:01.840 --> 32:03.560
<i>He was a lovely man.</i>

32:04.880 --> 32:06.520
<i>He was an engineer.</i>

32:06.520 --> 32:09.320
<i>Lenny used the depot workshop
of a weekend,</i>

32:09.320 --> 32:11.640
<i>um... to build his inventions.</i>

32:12.840 --> 32:14.800
<i>He was a brilliant welder.</i>

32:16.520 --> 32:17.960
<i>Bert, what happened to Lenny?</i>

32:17.960 --> 32:22.200
<i>The blast knocked an eight-tonne bus
on its side.</i>

32:23.600 --> 32:25.840
<i>The acetylene tank blew a hole
through the roof.</i>

32:25.840 --> 32:28.800
<i>They found it a 100 yards away. Jesus.</i>

32:28.800 --> 32:30.880
<i>He died on the way to hospital.</i>

32:32.200 --> 32:33.640
<i>It was written up...</i>

32:34.800 --> 32:36.640
<i>...as an accident.</i>

32:38.760 --> 32:40.080
<i>What do you think?</i>

32:40.080 --> 32:41.560
<i>He was hounded to death.</i>

32:42.600 --> 32:45.160
<i>Why was that?
Because of what happened to Bobby?</i>

32:45.160 --> 32:46.840
<i>Lenny killed himself.</i>

32:48.120 --> 32:50.840
<i>Everybody knew it, no-one said it.</i>

32:52.120 --> 32:54.240
<i>I should have helped him,</i>

32:54.240 --> 32:58.240
<i>but when someone
gets tagged a paedo,</i>

32:58.240 --> 33:00.040
<i>you don't, do you?</i>

33:04.880 --> 33:07.360
<i>And were they right? Did he...?</i>

33:08.680 --> 33:10.360
<i>Course not.</i>

33:11.520 --> 33:13.280
<i>Let me get you another pint, Bert...</i>

33:14.680 --> 33:16.000
<i>Mate, I'm so sorry.</i>

33:16.000 --> 33:17.440
<i>Fucking drunk...
I didn't see it.</i>

33:17.440 --> 33:18.920
<i>It was just clumsy.
I'll get you...</i>

33:18.920 --> 33:20.360
<i>Clumsy?
I'm sorry.</i>

33:20.360 --> 33:21.640
<i>Ooh.
JOE GRUNTS</i>

33:21.640 --> 33:24.560
<i>Now, you're fucking clumsy.</i>

33:27.720 --> 33:28.920
<i>JOE GROANS</i>

33:37.440 --> 33:40.600
<i>'And tragedy today
at a Liverpool bus depot.</i>

33:40.600 --> 33:43.240
<i>'A man thought to be
in his late forties...'</i>

33:43.240 --> 33:44.840
<i>'Did he abandon you?'</i>

33:44.840 --> 33:46.880
<i>Abandon?</i>

33:46.880 --> 33:49.080
<i>Joe, you know nothing about him.</i>

34:31.040 --> 34:32.640
<i>He's inside.</i>

34:32.640 --> 34:35.160
<i>Did Catherine ever mention a Bobby?</i>

34:35.160 --> 34:38.520
<i>A Bobby Morgan or... a Bobby Moran?</i>

34:38.520 --> 34:39.800
<i>No.</i>

34:39.800 --> 34:43.320
<i>And I don't feel comfortable
with you being here.</i>

34:43.320 --> 34:46.760
<i>Carl, I just told you,
the police released me.</i>

34:46.760 --> 34:47.800
<i>It was a wrongful arrest.</i>

34:47.800 --> 34:49.440
<i>I'm trying to find out
what happened...</i>

34:49.440 --> 34:50.720
<i>You abused Catherine.</i>

34:50.720 --> 34:53.000
<i>No, I didn't.
Catherine was ill.</i>

34:53.000 --> 34:54.560
<i>She withdrew the complaint.</i>

34:54.560 --> 34:56.560
<i>I was helping her
with some serious issues,</i>

34:56.560 --> 34:58.960
<i>and I want wanna help her now.
A little late for that.</i>

34:58.960 --> 35:00.680
<i>I don't think it's too late.</i>

35:00.680 --> 35:02.600
<i>I think it's important
how she's remembered.</i>

35:02.600 --> 35:04.360
<i>She deserves some dignity.</i>

35:04.360 --> 35:07.160
<i>The police, Carl,
have handled this so badly,</i>

35:07.160 --> 35:10.480
<i>I'm here to try
to find out the truth.</i>

35:12.520 --> 35:14.920
<i>Now, when I knew Catherine,
she kept a journal.</i>

35:14.920 --> 35:16.360
<i>She was religious about it,</i>

35:16.360 --> 35:18.240
<i>no matter what she was going through.</i>

35:18.240 --> 35:20.480
<i>Do you have any idea
if she still kept one or...</i>

35:20.480 --> 35:22.000
<i>where it might be?</i>

35:23.440 --> 35:25.600
<i>It might really help
in finding her killer, Carl.</i>

35:25.600 --> 35:27.640
<i>Police turned the house upside down.</i>

35:29.480 --> 35:33.640
<i>If they found a journal or whatever,
they didn't say.</i>

35:35.240 --> 35:36.760
<i>All right.</i>

35:41.080 --> 35:42.800
<i>Thank you for your time.</i>

35:42.800 --> 35:45.560
<i>There's just one more thing...</i>

35:46.720 --> 35:49.200
<i>It was a London agency</i>

35:49.200 --> 35:51.960
<i>that dealt with the recruitment
of the receptionist job.</i>

35:51.960 --> 35:53.960
<i>She was up in Liverpool.</i>

35:53.960 --> 35:55.760
<i>Do you know how she found out
about it?</i>

35:56.680 --> 36:00.120
<i>A letter.
I don't know who from.</i>

36:00.120 --> 36:02.440
<i>She wasn't sure about applying,</i>

36:02.440 --> 36:06.000
<i>but the guy who she was seeing
convinced her to go for it.</i>

36:06.000 --> 36:07.920
<i>Who was that?</i>

36:07.920 --> 36:10.320
<i>Her secret London lover.</i>

36:11.400 --> 36:14.400
<i>I think he wanted her
to move down there.</i>

36:14.400 --> 36:16.400
<i>They met a few years ago</i>

36:16.400 --> 36:19.560
<i>when he was working
at a hospital up here.</i>

36:19.560 --> 36:22.480
<i>Consultant, doctor, nurse?</i>

36:23.480 --> 36:24.600
<i>A doctor.</i>

36:24.600 --> 36:28.400
<i>She joked that he was...
good with his hands.</i>

36:28.400 --> 36:30.160
<i>Probably a surgeon.</i>

36:30.160 --> 36:31.960
<i>Rich, poor?</i>

36:31.960 --> 36:34.480
<i>She'd meet him at hotels.</i>

36:34.480 --> 36:36.200
<i>Rich, then.</i>

36:36.200 --> 36:37.480
<i>Probably no children.</i>

36:37.480 --> 36:40.240
<i>Do you know if they met
on weekdays or weekends?</i>

36:40.240 --> 36:42.000
<i>Weekends.</i>

36:42.000 --> 36:43.680
<i>Definitely no children.</i>

37:07.160 --> 37:09.400
<i>Welcome to Liverpool,
Detective Inspector.</i>

37:09.400 --> 37:10.560
<i>Sergeant.</i>

37:10.560 --> 37:13.360
<i>I followed him around here
from his hotel, but...</i>

37:13.360 --> 37:15.040
<i>he didn't go straight in.</i>

37:15.040 --> 37:17.240
<i>He walked past the house
three or four times.</i>

37:18.200 --> 37:19.360
<i>Er...</i>

37:22.960 --> 37:24.440
<i>Keep on him, yeah?</i>

37:24.440 --> 37:26.840
<i>Everywhere he goes
and everyone he sees.</i>

37:26.840 --> 37:28.920
<i>Yes, boss.
Good man.</i>

37:30.760 --> 37:33.840
<i>I knew his trail
would lead us to Catherine.</i>

37:35.880 --> 37:40.080
<i>So, he said,
"She was religious about it?"</i>

37:40.080 --> 37:44.080
<i>He was certain she kept a journal,
and that he needed to find it.</i>

37:44.080 --> 37:46.640
<i>And you told him you knew nothing
about it.</i>

37:47.680 --> 37:48.960
<i>Because I don't.</i>

37:52.560 --> 37:56.640
<i>What's the last image you have
of Catherine?</i>

37:58.920 --> 38:01.520
<i>Was she smiling?</i>

38:01.520 --> 38:05.160
<i>Walking into the room?
Eating breakfast? Laughing?</i>

38:06.480 --> 38:08.880
<i>Yeah, she was over by the...</i>

38:08.880 --> 38:10.680
<i>the window...</i>

38:10.680 --> 38:13.280
<i>um... arranging flowers.</i>

38:15.680 --> 38:16.880
<i>She was happy.</i>

38:16.880 --> 38:19.480
<i>You see, the last image we have
of Catherine</i>

38:19.480 --> 38:22.600
<i>is lying dead on a mortuary slab.</i>

38:22.600 --> 38:26.640
<i>This was a horrible,
sadistic, brutal murder!</i>

38:26.640 --> 38:29.840
<i>Now, if she was "religious"
about keeping a journal,</i>

38:29.840 --> 38:31.040
<i>there'd be a journal!</i>

38:32.080 --> 38:34.040
<i>Where is it?</i>

38:34.040 --> 38:35.600
<i>Listen...</i>

38:36.760 --> 38:40.160
<i>...perverting the course of justice
is an automatic prison sentence,</i>

38:40.160 --> 38:43.920
<i>and, believe me, you have no idea</i>

38:43.920 --> 38:47.040
<i>what prison would be like
for someone like you.</i>

38:50.040 --> 38:51.920
<i>I didn't think it was important.</i>

38:54.680 --> 38:57.840
<i>Catherine hadn't paid her share
of the rent, right?</i>

38:57.840 --> 39:01.120
<i>She was always late, always.</i>

39:02.720 --> 39:05.760
<i>I just got fed up with it.</i>

39:05.760 --> 39:07.480
<i>So, um...</i>

39:08.640 --> 39:12.520
<i>...when she was out, I, er...
took her laptop.</i>

39:14.280 --> 39:17.080
<i>I was going to tell her
she could have it back</i>

39:17.080 --> 39:19.000
<i>if she just paid up, you know?</i>

39:19.000 --> 39:21.160
<i>But she didn't come back.</i>

39:22.960 --> 39:25.520
<i>And where is this laptop?</i>

39:27.600 --> 39:30.600
<i>It's just in the cupboard outside.</i>

39:30.600 --> 39:32.040
<i>Shall I?</i>

39:32.040 --> 39:33.880
<i>Yeah, please, go and get it!</i>

39:42.760 --> 39:45.600
<i>RAILWAY TRACKS SCREECH</i>

39:59.000 --> 40:02.000
<i>This is all a bit cloak and dagger,
isn't it?</i>

40:02.000 --> 40:04.360
<i>Jesus, what happened to your face?
Did you get it?</i>

40:05.720 --> 40:06.920
<i>Here.</i>

40:10.120 --> 40:11.800
<i>What's this about, Joe?</i>

40:13.680 --> 40:18.440
<i>When Catherine applied
for the job of receptionist, she...</i>

40:19.680 --> 40:21.880
<i>I-I shredded her application
without reading it.</i>

40:21.880 --> 40:23.320
<i>I-I panicked. I...</i>

40:23.320 --> 40:25.600
<i>I saw her photograph,
and I just...</i>

40:25.600 --> 40:26.960
<i>I couldn't deal with it.</i>

40:26.960 --> 40:29.320
<i>Such a credit to the profession.</i>

40:29.320 --> 40:31.160
<i>You're right, though,</i>

40:31.160 --> 40:33.080
<i>Meena kept copies of everything.</i>

40:33.080 --> 40:34.920
<i>Best receptionist
to ever walk out on us.</i>

40:34.920 --> 40:37.560
<i>I still can't deal with it,
can you read it out to me, please?</i>

40:38.680 --> 40:41.720
<i>Which part?
Doesn't matter.</i>

40:41.720 --> 40:44.840
<i>Well, I always skip the irritating,
"why I want this job" part,</i>

40:44.840 --> 40:47.160
<i>go straight to the references,
work backwards.</i>

40:47.160 --> 40:49.200
<i>Here we are.</i>

40:49.200 --> 40:52.240
<i>Alison Kingsley, ward sister.</i>

40:52.240 --> 40:54.400
<i>Carl Ashley, medical technician.</i>

40:54.400 --> 40:56.400
<i>Dr Gerald Owens,
consultant neurologist...</i>

40:56.400 --> 40:57.960
<i>Gerald Owens?
Yep.</i>

40:57.960 --> 40:59.680
<i>Show me.</i>

41:02.520 --> 41:04.400
<i>That's Jack.</i>

41:06.920 --> 41:09.240
<i>Catherine was seeing Jack.</i>

41:09.240 --> 41:12.440
<i>He's involved in this somehow.
Is that the Dr Owens I've met?</i>

41:12.440 --> 41:14.080
<i>Yeah, yeah, he was best man
at my wedding.</i>

41:14.080 --> 41:16.280
<i>I've known him years, he...</i>

41:16.280 --> 41:20.320
<i>We met at med school, we were...
best pals all through uni.</i>

41:20.320 --> 41:22.640
<i>Mm, I found him a bit handsy.</i>

41:22.640 --> 41:25.200
<i>Why do you call him Jack
if his name's Gerald?</i>

41:25.200 --> 41:27.360
<i>It's nickname Jack,
"Jack The Lad".</i>

41:27.360 --> 41:28.800
<i>He was always chasing women.</i>

41:28.800 --> 41:32.200
<i>I think he's been lying to me
about Catherine all this time.</i>

41:32.200 --> 41:34.280
<i>He's been having an affair with her.</i>

41:34.280 --> 41:37.000
<i>And he persuaded her to apply
for the job that...</i>

41:37.000 --> 41:38.640
<i>Cos his name was on the reference,</i>

41:38.640 --> 41:40.960
<i>that... that's his humour,
that's him joking.</i>

41:40.960 --> 41:42.360
<i>Why, why would he do that?</i>

41:42.360 --> 41:44.240
<i>I don't know why he'd do it but... Listen...</i>

41:44.240 --> 41:47.440
<i>the police have been trying
to access your list to find evidence</i>

41:47.440 --> 41:49.720
<i>of abusing clients or
if any others have gone missing.</i>

41:49.720 --> 41:51.480
<i>It's all bullshit, though, it...</i>

41:51.480 --> 41:54.000
<i>Look, Catherine disappeared...</i>

41:55.040 --> 41:58.080
<i>...on the day that she called
our office, and...</i>

41:58.080 --> 42:00.480
<i>Oh, God, I wish I could've spoken
to her.</i>

42:00.480 --> 42:02.800
<i>I think he met up
with Catherine that night.</i>

42:02.800 --> 42:04.920
<i>Are you saying he killed her?</i>

42:04.920 --> 42:07.360
<i>Seriously?
No, but...</i>

42:07.360 --> 42:09.800
<i>Look, I know I'm only
making these connections,</i>

42:09.800 --> 42:13.040
<i>and-and it's not real but...</i>

42:13.040 --> 42:15.200
<i>he's the one that sent me
Bobby Morgan.</i>

42:15.200 --> 42:16.720
<i>Maybe he's the one manipulating him.</i>

42:16.720 --> 42:20.240
<i>Joe, you need to go to the police,
tell them everything, and go now.</i>

42:20.240 --> 42:24.640
<i>DISTANT SIRENS ECHOING</i>

42:27.120 --> 42:28.480
<i>Jack?</i>

42:29.640 --> 42:31.080
<i>Jack?</i>

43:25.760 --> 43:27.240
<i>DOOR OPENING</i>

43:28.360 --> 43:30.160
<i>Oh, sorry.
SHE YELPS</i>

43:30.160 --> 43:32.280
<i>I'm just collecting my things.</i>

43:33.560 --> 43:36.720
<i>You know, you should hang a sign
around your friend Jack's neck.</i>

43:36.720 --> 43:40.320
<i>"Warning, incapable of love
or affection".</i>

43:47.120 --> 43:49.880
<i>PHONE RINGING TONE</i>

43:55.600 --> 43:57.880
<i>PHONE RINGING</i>

43:58.880 --> 44:00.080
<i>Hello?</i>

44:00.080 --> 44:01.360
<i>Scanning now.</i>

44:03.200 --> 44:04.440
<i>Dr O'Loughlin.</i>

44:04.440 --> 44:05.880
<i>Yeah.</i>

44:05.880 --> 44:07.800
<i>'Back in London?</i>

44:07.800 --> 44:10.320
<i>'We saw you get on the train
at Liverpool,</i>

44:10.320 --> 44:13.160
<i>'so... that'd be my guess.'</i>

44:13.160 --> 44:15.400
<i>We've found
what you were looking for.</i>

44:15.400 --> 44:17.200
<i>Catherine's journal.</i>

44:18.640 --> 44:21.120
<i>'Yeah, I can understand why you
were so desperate to have it,</i>

44:21.120 --> 44:24.560
<i>'all those details of the affair
that you had with her.'</i>

44:25.800 --> 44:28.440
<i>We need you to come in, Joe.</i>

44:28.440 --> 44:31.360
<i>We're charging you with her murder.</i>

44:33.200 --> 44:36.720
<i>I didn't kill her, and I did
not have affair with her.</i>

44:36.720 --> 44:39.160
<i>Catherine was meticulous
with her journal -</i>

44:39.160 --> 44:42.600
<i>dates, times you met...
all the details.</i>

44:42.600 --> 44:45.840
<i>The night she disappeared
she met with Dr Owens.</i>

44:45.840 --> 44:47.560
<i>How'd you know that?</i>

44:47.560 --> 44:49.640
<i>Because he was the one having
an affair with her.</i>

44:49.640 --> 44:51.840
<i>'Jack Owens.'</i>

44:51.840 --> 44:55.200
<i>Oh, we know about his previous
relationship with Catherine.</i>

44:55.200 --> 44:57.240
<i>He told us.</i>

44:57.240 --> 44:59.120
<i>Previous relationship?</i>

44:59.120 --> 45:01.480
<i>'It ended. Two years ago.'</i>

45:01.480 --> 45:03.520
<i>He was a little late in the day</i>

45:03.520 --> 45:07.480
<i>with his confession but, er...
better late than never, eh?</i>

45:07.480 --> 45:10.200
<i>'And when he phoned it in,
he told me you were in Liverpool</i>

45:10.200 --> 45:12.240
<i>'and that he was worried...</i>

45:12.240 --> 45:14.360
<i>'about your state of mind.'</i>

45:14.360 --> 45:17.480
<i>He even told me that he
had arranged to meet Catherine</i>

45:17.480 --> 45:19.480
<i>that night, but he didn't go.</i>

45:19.480 --> 45:21.120
<i>He didn't meet her.</i>

45:21.120 --> 45:23.960
<i>He's lying. He-he's clearly lying.</i>

45:23.960 --> 45:27.960
